Class WarehouseGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • WarehouseGenerator

  • public class WarehouseGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    WarehouseGenerator is responsible for initialising the game map with the initial positions of the player and boxes, as well as generating the walls and goal locations for the level. The levels are created by taking a prototype depending on what level the player is on and then randomly placing a set of templates to create interesting levels.
